name: No Going Back.
description:
The only way for us is forward.
Going backwards is just staying in place.
Stuck at a stop.
And even then, everything else moves on without you.
There is only one direction whether you choose to lead or follow.
Take a rest, but there is no catching up. It's just continuing in your tracks.
